description:
&lt;p&gt;Looking for a challenge? We want to recruit a dynamic and experienced renal nurse to join our innovative team running nurse led chronic kidney disease CKD clinics. You will provide high quality clinical care for patients with CKD and deliver tailored education to empower patients to make choices when preparing for future treatment options such as transplantation and dialysis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This offers an exciting development opportunity with the potential for further career progression. You should be flexible, motivated, with excellent communication skills, have demonstrable post registration renal experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our team provides nurse led clinics at the Royal Free Hospital and across our three kidney care centres located in north and central London. You will be required to rotate between sites starting initially at Tottenham hale and there may be an opportunity to rotate to other renal specialities such as transplantation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Royal Free Hospital&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer Consultant and Nurse led CKD, pre Renal Replacement Therapy (RRT) and Transplant clinics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tottenham Hale Kidney and Diabetes Centre.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is one of the largest stand-alone dialysis and kidney care centres in Europe. It provides a 4 stationed dialysis unit including a 5 stationed supported care training area, and Consultant and Nurse led CKD, pre RRT, Transplant, PD and Diabetes clinics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;St Pancras Kidney and Diabetes Centre&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kidney Care unit with 30 dialysis stations with an additional 12 stationed supported self-care and home haemodialysis training unit. It offers consultant and nurse led CKD, pre RRT, PD and Home Haemodialysis clinics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Edgware Kidney Care Centre&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kidney Care Unit with 29 dialysis stations with on-site consultant and nurse led CKD, pre RRT, PD and transplant clinics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Joanne Henry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job Title: Lead Nurse Specialist Practice CKD and Hypertension.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address:joannehenry@nhs.net.&lt;/p&gt;
